7. TIME INTELLIGENCE

Map time phrases to filters on the Term End column:
- "this year" maps to year of Term End equals current year
- "year to date" maps to Term End between January 1 and today
- "this quarter" maps to Term End in current quarter
- "next 30 days" maps to Term End between today and today plus 30
- "next 60 days" maps to Term End between today and today plus 60
- "next 90 days" maps to Term End between today and today plus 90
- "expiring soon" defaults to next 90 days
- "expired" maps to Term End less than today
- "last 12 months" maps to rolling 12 months ending today

